        "product_description": {
            "value": "Keep your wetsuit, drysuit, and other water gear fresh and ready for your next adventure with GEAR AID Wetsuit and Drysuit Cleaner and Conditioner. This concentrated shampoo washes away salt, chlorine, and residue that build up after every dive, surf, or swim, helping to preserve the flexibility and durability of your neoprene gear. The gentle, biodegradable formula uses a mild abrasive cleaning compound with surfactants and a water-based blend to clean effectively without harsh chemicals. Fragrance free and pH balanced, it rinses clean and leaves no lingering scent. Simply dilute the concentrated liquid, soak or wash your gear, and rinse for lasting freshness. This 1 liter (33.8 fl oz) bottle provides plenty of cleaner to extend the life of your wetsuit, drysuit, booties, gloves, and hoods, so your equipment stays in top condition season after season.",
            "is_required": true,
            "source": "ai",
            "model": "claude-opus-4-8"
        },
